Titolo: Malicious (video game)

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Malicious (マリシアス, Marishiasu) is a download-only 3D action game developed and published by Alvion for the PlayStation 3 and the PlayStation Vita. Malicious was released on October 27, 2010 and is available to download from PlayStation Store in Japan. Because of the game's critical success, an enhanced port of the game was announced for the PlayStation Vita entitled Malicious Rebirth, featuring a new “Rebirth” chapter with new levels, new bosses and new moves.